graph TB
    subgraph MCPServer["RHOAI MCP Server (FastMCP)"]
        direction TB
        Server["MCP Server<br/>Transport: stdio / SSE / streamable-http<br/>Port: 8000/TCP"]
        PluginMgr["Plugin Manager<br/>(pluggy)"]
        K8sClient["K8s Client<br/>Auth: SA Token / Kubeconfig / Token"]
        Cache["Response Cache<br/>(TTL-based)"]
        PortFwd["Port Forward Manager<br/>(asyncio subprocess)"]

        Server -->|registers plugins| PluginMgr
        Server -->|uses| Cache
        PluginMgr -->|health checks via| K8sClient
    end

    subgraph DomainPlugins["Domain Plugins (10)"]
        direction LR
        Notebooks["Notebooks<br/>Workbenches"]
        Inference["Inference<br/>Model Serving"]
        Pipelines["Pipelines<br/>DSPA"]
        Connections["Connections<br/>S3 Secrets"]
        Storage["Storage<br/>PVCs"]
        Training["Training<br/>TrainJob"]
        ModelReg["Model Registry<br/>Models & Artifacts"]
        Quickstarts["Quickstarts<br/>50 Templates"]
        Projects["Projects<br/>Namespaces"]
        Prompts["Prompts<br/>18 Templates"]
    end

    subgraph CompositePlugins["Composite Plugins (4)"]
        direction LR
        ClusterExplore["Cluster Exploration<br/>Summary & Diagnostics"]
        TrainingWF["Training Workflows<br/>Unified Interface"]
        NeuralNav["Neural Navigator<br/>Model Recommendations"]
        Meta["Meta / Tool Discovery<br/>Intent Matching"]
    end

    PluginMgr -->|loads| DomainPlugins
    PluginMgr -->|loads| CompositePlugins

    DomainPlugins -->|CRUD operations| K8sClient
    CompositePlugins -->|orchestrates| DomainPlugins

    %% External interactions
    Agent["AI Agent<br/>(Claude / ChatGPT)"] -->|MCP Protocol| Server
    K8sClient -->|HTTPS/6443| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server"]

    subgraph ExternalClients["External Service Clients"]
        NNClient["Neural Navigator Client<br/>(httpx)"]
        MRClient["Model Registry Client<br/>(httpx)"]
    end

    NeuralNav -->|uses| NNClient
    ModelReg -->|uses| MRClient
    ModelReg -->|uses| PortFwd

    NNClient -->|HTTP/8000| NNBackend["Neural Navigator<br/>Backend Service"]
    MRClient -->|HTTP/8080<br/>HTTPS/8443| MRService["Model Registry<br/>Service"]

    %% CRDs consumed
    K8sClient -->|watches| DSC["DataScienceCluster CR"]
    K8sClient -->|CRUD| NotebookCR["Kubeflow Notebook CR"]
    K8sClient -->|CRUD| ISVC["InferenceService CR"]
    K8sClient -->|CRUD| TrainJobCR["TrainJob CR"]
    K8sClient -->|CRUD| DSPA["DSPA CR"]

    %% Styling
    style MCPServer fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:2px
    style DomainPlugins fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px
    style CompositePlugins fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100,stroke-width:2px
    style ExternalClients fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c62828,stroke-width:2px

    style Server fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style PluginMgr fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style K8sClient fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style Agent fill:#9c27b0,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,color:#fff
    style NNBackend fill:#f5a623
    style MRService fill:#f5a623
    style DSC fill:#7ed321
    style NotebookCR fill:#7ed321
    style ISVC fill:#7ed321
    style TrainJobCR fill:#7ed321
    style DSPA fill:#7ed321
